 of front doors from a splittie he is having restored.--This set of front
 doors are complete--handles--windows, etc. everything is there--Except, for
 some stupid reason, "The Restorers"? --Went and cut off, On Both front
 doors, the Top hinge. Ergo,both doors are missing their top hinge--No doubt
 this does decrease their value. Other then the missing top hinge--both door
 are fine. Do not want to make an issue about this as to the "Why"?--But it
 happened--If you have any ideas just e-mail me, and I can relay the info to
